<BaseLayout lang="en" current="electricite" title="Electricity" description="Passionate electrical installations , our intervention team identifies the problem as quickly as possible , so that your plants can function optimally. Low curr">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-content">
        <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/en/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/en/electricity/">Electricity</a></div>
        <div style="margin: -2rem -2rem 2rem -2rem; height: 220px; background: url('/images/electricien.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius-lg) var(--radius-lg);"></div>
        <h1>Electricity</h1>
        <p>Passionate electrical installations , our intervention team identifies the problem as quickly as possible , so that your plants can function optimally.</p>

<p>Low current , high current , wiring and data protection techniques , all this has no secrets for us!</p>

<p>Your electrical installations are installed , upgraded and maintained by us and according to your comfort. Our priorities when working are quality and safety, two core values ​​for a successful electric mission!</p>

<p><a href="/en/contact">Contact us</a> without further ado, we offer a suitable solution with fast delivery and unbeatable prices!</p>

      </div>
    </div>
